---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Terms & Conditions | Real BMI"
    description="Review the terms and conditions for using the Real BMI precision health calculator."
>
    <Navbar />
    <main class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
        <a href="/en" class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--foreground)] flex items-center gap-2 hover:translate-x-[-4px] transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" /></svg>
            Return Home
        </a>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase">Terms and Conditions</h1>
        <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--muted-foreground)] leading-relaxed space-y-8 text-xl font-bold">
            <p>
                When you step onto <span class="text-[var(--foreground)]">Real BMI</span>, you are entering a professional environment dedicated to your health. These terms are our way of ensuring that this environment remains safe, accurate, and useful for everyone.
            </p>
            <p>
                By using this tool, you acknowledge that while we strive for clinical-grade precision, the results are for <span class="text-[var(--foreground)] tracking-tight">informational purposes only.</span> This instrument is here to empower you, but it should not replace the deep, personalized advice of a healthcare professional.
            </p>
            <p>
                We ask that you use this tool respectfully and for the purpose for which it was built: personal health awareness. Our promise is to maintain the highest standards of availability and accuracy, and by using the site, you agree to join us in making data-driven wellness a standard for all.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-[var(--border)] italic opacity-60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                "Accuracy is our standard. Your well-being is our goal." — Real BMI
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
